Git Utils. Speeding up your commits.
--------------

PURPOSE:
--------------
Tools written just for speeding up my work.

INSTALLATION:
--------------
Copy it to ~/bin or /usr/bin. Users of other UNIXes: check path of bash.

NOTES:
--------------
Any parameters given to the gitcommit will be parameters of git commit in each dir.

